descriptor.long_desc: Amma's Pastries is a F&B-Casual Dining outlet that serves delicious and freshly-baked pastries. The atmosphere is warm and inviting, with friendly staff and a relaxed atmosphere. Amma's Pastries is the perfect place to enjoy a sweet treat or a light meal. Whether you're looking for a quick snack or a full meal, Amma's Pastries has something for everyone.

It is a great place to enjoy a delicious meal with friends and family. The menu includes a variety of cakes, pies, tarts, cupcakes, and other desserts. The atmosphere is cozy and inviting, with a warm and friendly staff. The desserts are made with fresh ingredients and are sure to satisfy any sweet tooth. Cake Junction also offers catering services for special occasions. Whether you are looking for a quick snack or a full meal, Cake Junction is the perfect place to satisfy your cravings.
